佔他人之不動產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/111%2c%e5%af%a9%e7%b0%a1%2c37%2c20220128%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,111,審簡,37,20220128,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"審簡","JNO":"37","JDATE":"20220128","JTITLE":"竊盜"}